Speaker 2: Okay, can I get your phone number so I can look at your account?

Speaker 1: Yeah, 847-530-4337, and there's no way you're going to see the words Sidenafil because absolutely I did not say that word, I have a hard time saying it, I ordered the Viagra AGV, that's what I called for.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: And that ain't what I've got in my hand right now and I'm not very happy, you're lucky I don't swear, so I won't use any profanity because I don't swear but I'm not happy, I waited 5 days for this new super AGV, works in 11 minutes and I'm all excited, finally I get it and I go open it up and it's Sidenafil, which I get from my own doctor for $3.20, 30 of them.

Speaker 2: Yeah, no, absolutely, I understand your frustration sir, do you mind telling me what it says on the actual tablet?

Speaker 1: It says Sidenafil in capital letters, 100 milligram tablet, generic for Viagra, take one tablet by mouth, one hour before sex as needed, do not take more than one dose in 24 hours.

Speaker 1: Huh?

Speaker 2: But I do want to clarify, sir, it will, Sidenafil is the active ingredient in all of Viagra, so don't let that throw you off, but this next order that I'm sending you will be a replacement order, obviously at no cost, and I'll expedite the shipping, and of course you can keep the ones you have there, it's just generic Viagra through Pfizer, but the one I'm sending you will be the new and improved AGV.

Speaker 1: Okay, I do apologize if that happens.

Speaker 2: Thank you, but that's what I ordered, how could they screw up an order like that?

Speaker 1: I'm just saying, that's exactly what I ordered, I've already got this one here, I've got 30 of them here, sitting around here, because they're not as effective and they haven't been doing very good, and I thought, oh, this is good, super Viagra, new and improved, I can't wait to get it, and sure enough, I get the wrong stinking order.

Speaker 2: Well, if you could rush it out, it would be great.

Speaker 1: I will, sir, I do apologize, I think the AGV is just selling so quickly, I don't know how the pharmacy screwed that up, but I'll make sure you get the AGV on this next order, okay?
